{"title":"梅农声明","authors":["袁水拍"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":4,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅农声明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁水拍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为新华社希望达赖发表第一人称的声明，因此这次声明是以第一人称发表的。　——梅农答复西方记者语。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一个声明——第三人称，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二个声明——第一人称。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借问梅农先生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为何花样翻新？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人希望第一人称，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此就用第一人称，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要什么人称，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有什么人称，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要什么声明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有什么声明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的是纸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的是笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要素斋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就不给荤腥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饭馆包办筵席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敝处包办声明。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}